name: The Window - Hahnemuhle Photorag
description:
This is my second photographic release, titled 'The Window'.

It's an edition of 6, on Hahnemuhle Photorag paper, again the photo doesn't catch the soft finish very well.

This photo was taken on a tour of underground tunnels in Manchester in complete darkness other than light from our torches.

Title: The Window
Media: Hahnemuhle Photorag 
Edition: 6
Size: 10.5 x 14" (approx)
P&P: UK £4, everywhere else £6

name: Fatum Est Eternus - No. 1

name: Mystery Sale
description:
So i've just got a few old pieces back from a gallery that never went anywhere.  Included were four pieces (probably faces) on (probably) cardboard, of the kind i used to give away as freebies.

I've no idea what these pieces are of, as they came individually packed and ready to send.

So it's a complete lottery, just pay postage, and one at random will be yours!
